Design System Rules
Never default Tailwind blue/indigo — always use brand tokens via inline style or Tailwind config
Shadows: layered, color-tinted with low opacity (e.g., 0 4px 24px rgba(3,98,128,0.15))
Headings: Montserrat 300, tight tracking
Script accents: Great Vibes for section titles
Images: always add gradient overlay + mix-blend-multiply color layer
Hover states on all interactive elements
Mobile-first responsive (stack to single col on mobile)
Depth system: bg #ecede7 → white cards → dark #405f7d sections
Verification Steps
node serve.mjs (background) → serves at http://localhost:3000
node screenshot.mjs http://localhost:3000 — full page
Screenshot each subpage: /nosotros.html, /consultoria.html, /paquetes.html, /catalogos.html
Read each screenshot with Read tool, compare against brief wireframes
Fix layout, spacing, color, and typography issues
Minimum 2 rounds per page before moving on
Final mobile viewport check: node screenshot.mjs http://localhost:3000 mobile --width=390 --height=844